This is a simple command line note taker app.
You can add, remove, read and list notes using command line.

Using Application with Command Line
    Adding a note:
        Run " node app.js add --title="Budget" --body="5k for tomatoes" "
        Requirements:
            Title and body are required
            Duplicate notes can not be added

    Reading a note:
        Run " node app.js read --title="Budget" "

    Listing notes:
        Run " node app.js list "

    Removing a note:
        Run " node app.js remove --title="Budget" "